d;=\"\"&gt;datalist（选项列表）&lt;br&nbsp;style=\"word-wrap:\"&nbsp;break-word;=\"\"&gt;w3c赋予的解释：&lt;br&nbsp;style=\"word-wrap:\"&nbsp;break-word;=\"\"&gt;&amp;lt;datalist&amp;gt;&nbsp;标签定义选项列表。请与&nbsp;input&nbsp;元素配合使用该元素，来定义&nbsp;input&nbsp;可能的值。&lt;br&nbsp;style=\"word-wrap:\"&nbsp;break-word;=\"\"&nbsp;color:=\"\"&nbsp;rgb(68,=\"\"&nbsp;68,=\"\"&nbsp;68);=\"\"&nbsp;font-family:=\"\"&nbsp;tahoma,=\"\"&nbsp;helvetica,=\"\"&nbsp;simsun,=\"\"&nbsp;sans-serif;=\"\"&nbsp;line-height:=\"\"&nbsp;21px;=\"\"&nbsp;text-align:=\"\"&nbsp;-webkit-auto;=\"\"&gt;&lt;font&nbsp;color=\"#222222\"&nbsp;style=\"word-wrap:\"&nbsp;break-word;=\"\"&nbsp;font-family:=\"\"&nbsp;tahoma,=\"\"&nbsp;helvetica,=\"\"&nbsp;simsun,=\"\"&nbsp;sans-serif;=\"\"&nbsp;line-height:=\"\"&nbsp;21px;=\"\"&nbsp;text-align:=\"\"&nbsp;-webkit-auto;=\"\"&gt;datalist&nbsp;及其选项不会被想显示出来，它仅仅是合法的输入值列表。&lt;br&nbsp;style=\"word-wrap:\"&nbsp;break-word;=\"\"&nbsp;color:=\"\"&nbsp;rgb(68,=\"\"&nbsp;68,=\"\"&nbsp;68);=\"\"&nbsp;font-family:=\"\"&nbsp;tahoma,=\"\"&nbsp;helvetica,=\"\"&nbsp;simsun,=\"\"&nbsp;sans-serif;=\"\"&nbsp;line-height:=\"\"&nbsp;21px;=\"\"&nbsp;text-align:=\"\"&nbsp;-webkit-auto;=\"\"&gt;&lt;font&nbsp;color=\"#222222\"&nbsp;style=\"word-wrap:\"&nbsp;break-word;=\"\"&nbsp;font-family:=\"\"&nbsp;tahoma,=\"\"&nbsp;helvetica,=\"\"&nbsp;simsun,=\"\"&nbsp;sans-serif;=\"\"&nbsp;line-height:=\"\"&nbsp;21px;=\"\"&nbsp;text-align:=\"\"&nbsp;-webkit-auto;=\"\"&gt;请使用&nbsp;input&nbsp;元素的&nbsp;list&nbsp;属性来绑定&nbsp;datalist。&lt;br&nbsp;style=\"word-wrap:\"&nbsp;break-word;=\"\"&gt;&lt;div&nbsp;style=\"word-wrap:\"&nbsp;break-word;=\"\"&nbsp;overflow-x:=\"\"&nbsp;hidden;=\"\"&nbsp;overflow-y:=\"\"&nbsp;margin-top:=\"\"&nbsp;10px;=\"\"&nbsp;margin-right:=\"\"&nbsp;0px;=\"\"&nbsp;margin-bottom:=\"\"&nbsp;margin-left:=\"\"&nbsp;padding-top:=\"\"&nbsp;padding-right:=\"\"&nbsp;padding-bottom:=\"\"&nbsp;5px;=\"\"&nbsp;padding-left:=\"\"&nbsp;background-image:=\"\"&nbsp;url(http:=\"\"&nbsp;bbs.phphubei.com=\"\"&nbsp;static